---

<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="container about-inner">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <span class="section-index">01 /</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">About</h2>
      <span class="section-rule"></span>
    </div>
    <div class="about-layout reveal reveal-delay-1">
      <p class="about-lead">
        IT Engineer with a background in service and project management, aspiring to
        contribute organizational talents and proven expertise to leading companies in
        the luxury and tech sectors.
      </p>
      <p class="about-body">
        Highly curious individual with a strong desire for continuous learning and
        professional growth in dynamic environments. Experienced in Agile
        methodologies, data analytics, and service delivery optimization — I believe
        the best solutions come from understanding both the data and the people behind it.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background-color: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .about-layout {
    max-width: 780px;
  }

  .about-lead {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .about-body {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: var(--color-ink-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .about {
      padding: 3.5rem 0;
    }

    .about-lead {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }

    .about-body {
      font-size: 0.9375rem;
    }
  }
</style>
